desc: Donate to Vote! Raise funds for the Rotary Foundation by stuffing the ballot box for which DG you would like dunked at the Rotary District 5110 Celebration Street Party in Corvallis, Oregon, on 4/29/23. A fundraiser by the Rotary Club of Greater Corvallis.

layout.text: Dunk A DG - District Celebration Street Party - Corvallis 4/29/22
Donate to Vote! All donations will be sent to the Rotary Foundation. Get Votes and stuff the ballot box to choose the District 5110 DG to be DUNKED!
